<s> Hunter Environmental Services Inc. said it reached a preliminary accord on the sale of its environmental consulting and services business for about $ 40 million and assumption of related debt . </s>
<s> The buyer was n't identified . </s>
<s> The company said it also is making progress in negotiating the buy-out of its design division by management . </s>
<s> In addition , Hunter said it will use proceeds from a private placement of $ 8 million of preferred shares to purchase an interest in a start-up company to underwrite environmental impairment insurance . </s>
<s> Hunter wants to concentrate its resources on the insurance business and on a project to store hazardous wastes in salt domes . </s>
